{"type":"FeatureCollection","data_type":"Dataset","url_type":null,"permissions":[{"permissions":{"download":true,"view":true},"group_id":"everyone"}],"classification":null,"title":"\nHK public art\n","count":10,"stream_id":48941,"contributor":{"url":"http://geocommons.com/users/11444","name":"platial"},"data_attributes":null,"calculation_params":null,"icon_link":null,"link":"http://geocommons.com/overlays/48941.json","extent":[114.158,22.282,114.172,22.2937],"geometry_types":["point"],"unique_name":null,"name":"\nHK public art\n","feature_count":10,"description":"\nA Map by Cornofsculpture\n\n\n","next_feature":null,"is_raster":false,"short_classification":"Y","stats":{},"features":[{"properties":{"name":"The Flux《雨後‧太陽‧潮水》玻璃磚及金屬，安畢妍2004 ( 國際金融中心二期 天台平台)","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0447i_2_.JPG\">雕塑色彩繽紛，實際也是採光的天窗，並利用建築物在晚間發出的燈光，延續雕塑的欣賞性。造形像多把剪刀，比喻韓國文化中生命的不同文化階段，例如嬰出生時猷剪臍帶、長大時剪髮…，再而引申為生命的片斷。<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty59y3033"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.15807724,22.2845893982]}},{"properties":{"name":"Brunt1074《焦1074》混合物料,  郭孟浩2005 ( 香港大會堂內 )","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0431i.JPG\">作品位於香港大會堂近詢問處的牆壁上，是以火燻黑了的塑膠及動物骨頭組合而成，質感特別。<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty59ch9eb"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.161875248,22.2822266289]}},{"properties":{"name":"Conceal《隱》銅，劉有權1991 ( 香港藝術館戶外平台 )","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0351i.JPG\">雕塑的下部是一個肌肉發達之強壯軀體，上部呈三角形；上下部配合成強烈對比，好像有強大外來力量正壓著巨人，令人有壓迫和掙扎感，從作品中看見人們面對壓力與無助。<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty4wq0vyh"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.172110558,22.2933451949]}},{"properties":{"name":"Double Oval《對環》銅，享利摩爾1975 (怡和大廈東側 )","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0440i.JPG\">造型似兩片斜放的貝殼，在不同的角度觀看，都有不同變化。雕塑的圓孔與怡和大廈相呼應，是一件成功的環境雕塑。<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty57pdo11"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.159729481,22.2829066738]}},{"properties":{"name":"Flying Frenchman《翱翔的法國人》銅，凱撒1992 ( 香港文化中心旁 )","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0309i.JPG\">雕塑是卡地亞送贈香港，媒介由金屬片廢料焊接而成，凱撒花了三年時間製造，造型的靈感來自希臘神話，看起來像失去一邊翅膀，表現出不平衡感，有如問人我的另一翅膀去了那裏似的，又似一個接受挑戰的勇士。寓意香港人可自由飛翔。你又有何看法呢？\r\n\r\n你對一件鍛羽作品安置於面向維港，有何意見？<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty574st56"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.170200825,22.2932955604]}},{"properties":{"name":"Oval with points《尖環》銅，享利摩爾1974 ( 中環交易廣場 )","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0486i.JPG\">雕塑形態脹滿堅實，充滿力量，中央兩點在環中幾乎相連，令人感到相匯點的交流，加上作品像中國人生財的「8」字，義意上與附近的香港交易廣場互相呼應。<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty4z6uj0e"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.158120155,22.2841327316]}},{"properties":{"name":"Pompous General《橫行將軍》銅，張義1984 ( 香港太空館旁 )","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0354i_5_.JPG\">  超現實主意作品，形似蟹的橫行，但其八隻爪腳又像人腳般，頭頂部位又不像眼，但又像女性乳房，據張義的解讀，認為像甚麼也不重要，觀者有很大的自由空間去發揮想像力。\r\n你的想像力可以和大家分享嗎？\r\n歡迎討論賜教\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty518yx5o"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.172164202,22.2936827089]}},{"properties":{"name":"Silhouettes of City Life《城市剪影》銅，馮永基1997 ( 大會堂愛丁堡廣場 )","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0401i.JPG\">這些簡單的人物及動物剪影置於路邊椅旁，原意是防止遊人睡臥，但佈局巧妙，形態多變，是值得回味的公共藝術雕塑。<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty4uyokfj"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.161746502,22.2820479305]}},{"properties":{"name":"Tablet《銘》銅，張義1990 ( 香港藝術館戶外平台 )","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0343i.JPG\">由看似遠古與現代的符號組合而成，這些符號又似中國古代象形文字、人體器官、史前動物或篆書文字，令人有無限聯想。<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty54jfwzq"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.172164202,22.2936827089]}},{"properties":{"name":"Tai Chi Series-Single Whip Dep《單鞭下勢》青銅，朱銘 1986 ( 中環交易廣場側 )","description":"Posted by Cornofsculpture<img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/img/2008/02/3/CIMG0476i_2_.JPG\">這座雕塑是朱銘的太極系列之一，造型捕捉了太極拳的特點與氣氛。雕塑四面環水，目的是防止遊人攀爬破壞。<a title=\"Built for Community Mapping\" href=\"http://www.platial.com\"><img src=\"http://media.geocommons.com/platial/images/logotype_small.jpg\"></a>","id":"a63ty56mdt27"},"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"Point","coordinates":[114.157626629,22.28434121]}}],"is_temporal":false,"author":{"url":"http://www.platial.com/map/84197","metadata":null,"contact_name":"cornofsculpture","contact_address":null,"source":"platial:cornofsculpture","contact_phone":null},"source":"http://www.platial.com/map/84197","pagination":{"sort":null,"start":0,"total":10,"limit":1000000},"state":"complete","tags":"platial,platial:id=84197,platial:user=cornofsculpture","published":"2010-04-27T16:00:00Z","id":48941}